Description:
Rare Finding, Private Setting, 50 Acres 30 Mins West Of Ballarat
This established mixed use farming property is located only 5 minutes North of Clunes on Tullaroop Creek. Consisting of 50 acres of rich volcanic soil with substantial infrastructure. This property would suit most rural pursuits. The home comprises 4 bedrooms, large open plan family, lounge and dining with cathedral ceilings. Fantastic kitchen with huge larder and solar hot water service. The outside working improvements include an almost new set of steel cattle yards with vets crush and race, two stand shearing shed, machinery shed, hay shed and a large silo. The property is watered via bore and troughs plus a stock domestic pump right from Birch's Creek. Divided into 4 main paddocks with electric offsets and strategic shelter belts, philaris and clover pastures. Located at the end of a quiet country road, this property would ideally suit dog breeders as no other homes within one kilometere. This would allow the council to look favourably upon any permit application. The property would also suit other small hobby farm pursuits, including alpacas, goats or a few head of cattle. Full frontage to permanent Birch's Creek.
Insights: 11 other 4 bedroom house in CLUNES have recently been sold.

Description:
1414m2 Fully Serviced Block
Located in the township of Clunes, 100m from the Clunes Primary School, this elevated block overlooks the township with views to the North and West. Comprising 1414m2, this is a prime building allotment and should not be missed. Town water, sewerage and power pass the property.
Clunes is one of Victoria's oldest towns (Circa 1839) and retains most of its old world charm. Wesley College Junior Campus is located in the town which creates a stream of visitors on a weekly basis.

Description:
Sensational Renovation In The Heart Of Clunes
Yes, seeing is believing! The owners of this beautiful period home have rejuvenated it to exacting standards. From the front gate to the rear cottage garden and veggie plots, this 3 bedroom home will impress. The Baltic pine polished floors are stunning and add to the character and charm. Other features include an electric wall oven and hot plates, bathroom with claw foot bath, wood heater in the open plan living area and French doors which open out to a sensational entertainment area with pergola and built in BBQ. The gardens are landscaped and boast award winning roses and there is a large double garage with workshop. Located within easy walking distance to the Wesley College campus, local train station and the main shopping precinct, the home could also be used as a holiday rental as it has minimal maintenance. Inspect today!

Great character, wondrous history, two titles!

The three bedroom home boasts two living areas offering potential for a fourth bedroom. Each room is spacious and captures great natural light. The extension at the rear of the abode grants choices of a studio, office or workshop. The property holds two separate titles both approximately 1000m2. There is vast space for gardens, animals or additional shedding to be added to the existing. On the fringe of the historic township of Clunes and across the road from the train-station this lovely property is sure to sell fast.

Description:
High & dry, sitting quietly on fringe of Clunes.
This delightful home is on the north side of Clunes with only three minutes to the main street of town. On a quiet strip this extremely tidy abode has so much to offer. This three bedroom residence has been renovated and extended which is sure to please. A new kitchen is one surprise the property has to offer with modern appliances we all demand. The bathroom was wonderfully renovated last year. There is a separate dining and lounge so the residence is far larger than it appears from the road. Entertaining flows well from each room out to the pergola/bbq area. Shedding and car coverage is amply supplied with a carport and a large 9x6m garage. Sitting on an extra large allotment your family will have so much room for outdoor fun and games. At this realistic price, don't be late.
